\begin{align*} 1 &= a^{-1}a \tag{by definition of inverse}\\   &= a^{-1}(ax) \tag{since $ax = a$, and symmetry of $=$} \\   &= (a^{-1}a)x \tag{by associativity} \\   &= 1x \tag{by definition of inverse} \\   &= x.  \tag{by definition of identity} \end{align*} 
